        <li style="margin-top:14pt; margin-left:59pt; line-height:normal; padding-left:13pt; font-family:Roboto; font-size:13.5pt; font-weight:bold; background-color:#ffffff;">COUTNTERFETTING PRODUCTS<ol class="small-roman" type="i" style="margin-right:0pt; margin-left:0pt; padding-left:0pt;">
                <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"> packaging Depot Store Technovations Private Limited firmly prohibits the listing of any fake goods on the packaging Depot Store Platform. OEM agrees to accept, be bound by, and fully comply with this section by accessing, browsing, or otherwise using the Platform or the Services, including listing products. OEM may do so on their own behalf or through representatives in order to offer products for sale through the Platform.<ol class="lower-alpha" type="a" style="margin-right:0pt; margin-left:0pt; padding-left:0pt;">
                        <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; background-color:#ffffff;">&quot; "Counterfeit product" refers to any fake, replica, illegally produced item that has been copied to pass as the genuine article, bootlegged, or other-wise may infringe upon the intellectual property rights of a third party</li>
                    </ol>
                </li>
                <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"> packaging Depot Store retains the right to remove, suspend, or re-strict listings that might include fake goods and/or that might transgress the Platform's terms of use and prod-uct listing policy.</li>
                <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt;">In order to prove the authenticity of the products in their listing(s), OEM(s) may be required to provide documentation such as invoices or any other pertinent document, as well as a notarized declaration stating that the products under their listing(s) are genuine and authentic. The OEM's listing(s) may be suspended or cancelled if the aforementioned documentation is not provided within 72 hours.</span>.</li>
                <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt;">If the OEM's listing(s) are discovered to be for counter-feit goods, We reserve the right to take any necessary action, including but not limited to suspending or termi-nating the OEM's account, removing any and all of the OEM's product listings, withholding or forfeiting OEM payments, and other measures that may be deemed necessary. This shall be done without admitting any lia-bility and without impairing the expressly reserved

                    rights, remedies, or defenses of the Platform with packaging Depot Store. In addition, third party right holders may inde-pendently bring civil and criminal lawsuits against the OEMs listing such counterfeit goods.</span>.</li>
                
            </ol>
        </li>
    </ol>

    <ol class="numberText" start="5"  type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt;">
        <li style="margin-top:14pt; margin-left:59pt; line-height:normal; padding-left:13pt; font-family:Roboto; font-size:13.5pt; background-color:#ffffff;">AUDITS
            <ol class="small-roman" type="i" style="margin-right:0pt; margin-left:0pt; padding-left:0pt;">
                <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt;">i. In order to verify OEM adherence to these Terms, We may, at Our Sole Discretion, conduct random audits of the Shipments handed over to Logistic Partner for on-ward delivery to the Consignee. If it is determined or if we believe in our reasonable opinion that the Shipment or Products do not comply with applicable laws and/or do not have reasonable packaging, we may, in our sole discretion, levy penalty charges, as communicated to you from time to time, or take such other actions against you as listed under sub clause (ii) below, with-out limiting other rights available to us under these Terms or under applicable laws.</span></li>
                <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt;">We may be allowed to take one or more of the follow-ing actions at our sole discretion;<ol class="lower-alpha" type="a" style="margin-right:0pt; margin-left:0pt; padding-left:0pt;">
                        <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; background-color:#ffffff;"> issue a warning letter to the OEM;</li>
                        <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; background-color:#ffffff;">The higher of (a) INR 1000/- (Rupees One Thou-sand Only), (b) an amount equal to the total in-voice value of the audited shipment, (c) any other amount specified under applicable law, shall be levied on the OEM for each such non-compli-ance. This applies to both losses incurred by us and non-inclusion of a hard copy of the invoice in the shipment;</li>
                        <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; background-color:#ffffff;"> For any non-compliance other than those listed in Clause 3(ii)(b) above, the OEM will be held liable for the greater of (a) 2 (two) times the product's value or (b) the amount equal to the total invoice value for each such non-compliance;</li>
                        <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; background-color:#ffffff;">deactivate or suspend a OEM's account on the Platform, with or without giving any notice to the OEM; and/or</li>
                        <li style="margin-left:23pt;  padding-left:13pt; background-color:#ffffff;">such other action which we may deem fit in our sole discretion</li>
                    </ol>
                </li>
            </ol>
        </li>
    </ol>
    <p style="margin-top:14pt; margin-left:144pt;  line-height:normal; font-size:13.5pt; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:Roboto;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <ol class="numberText" start="6"  type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt;">
        <li style="margin-top:14pt; margin-left:59pt; line-height:normal; padding-left:13pt; font-family:Roboto; font-size:13.5pt; background-color:#ffffff;"><strong>PLATFORM FEES/CHARGES&nbsp;</strong>
            <ol class="small-roman" type="i" style="margin-right:0pt; margin-left:0pt; padding-left:0pt;">
                <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt;">i. In consideration of the platform provided by packaging Depot Store to the OEM, the OEM will be required to pay a fee (re-ferred to as “packaging Depot Store Fee” ) to packaging Depot Store. It is hereby clarified that the packaging Depot Store Fee shall be calculated on the total invoice value of the Order.</li>
                    <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt;">The applicable packaging Depot Store Fee shall be as packaging Depot Store may from time to time communicate to the OEM(s) through the Platform or through such other method of commu-nication as packaging Depot Store may determine in its sole discre-tion. The OEM shall be responsible for routinely verify-ing such packaging Depot Store Fee. If you use the Platform in the future, it will be assumed that you have accepted the packaging Depot Store Fee change.</li>
                        <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt;">packaging Depot Store will send the OEM an invoice for the packaging Depot Store Fee, and the OEM will pay packaging Depot Store for that invoice. OEM acknowledges that only the OEM shall be in charge of seeing that the packaging Depot Store Fee is given to the packaging Depot Store. OEM permits packaging Depot Store to make adjustments and deduct such packaging Depot Store Fees from amounts received or re-received from the Retailer in accordance with the settlement procedures outlined in the Payment and Settlement Services Agreement.</li>
                <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt;">The packaging Depot Store Fee will be subject to any applicable taxes under current law. If required by applicable law, OEM shall deduct income tax as appropriate from packaging Depot Store's payments, unless packaging Depot Store submits a nil/re-duced withholding certificate. By supplying a proper and timely certificate of withholding as required by the relevant law, OEM shall remit the withholding taxes to the appropriate tax authorities and permit packaging Depot Store to claim a tax credit.</li>
                <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt;"> packaging Depot Store will bill the OEM extra fees for any extra ser-vices it offers or for services it does not include in the packaging Depot Store platform. OEM hereby authorizes packaging Depot Store to adjust the charges from the receivable that are due and payable to OEM by packaging Depot Store. packaging Depot Store shall be entitled to recover/deduct such additional charges from the amount collected or received by packaging Depot Store from the Re-tailer. Such settlement shall be made in accordance with the settlement provision of the Payment and Set-tlement Services. packaging Depot Store may enter into a separate

                    agreement with the OEM to provide these additional services if packaging Depot Store so desires.</li>
                <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt;"> packaging Depot Store reserves the right to impose penalties or late payment fees in the event that the OEM is late in pay-ing any amounts owed to packaging Depot Store, as well as cancella-tion fees in the event that the OEM cancels any orders. OEM gives packaging Depot Store permission to adjust or deduct any penalties, late payment fees, or cancellation fees from the receivables packaging Depot Store owes OEM. According to the settlement procedure outlined in the Payment and Set-tlement Services herein, such settlement will be carried out.</li>
            </ol>
        </li>
        <li style="margin-left:59pt; line-height:normal; padding-left:13pt; font-family:Roboto; font-size:13.5pt; background-color:#ffffff;"><strong>packaging Depot Store SERVICES</strong>
            <ol class="small-roman" type="i" style="margin-right:0pt; margin-left:0pt; padding-left:0pt;">
                <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; background-color:#ffffff;"><strong><u>Standard Platform Services</u></strong>
                    <ol class="lower-alpha" type="a" style="margin-right:0pt; margin-left:0pt; padding-left:0pt;">
                        <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt;"> As long as you abide by these OEM Terms, you may list Products for sale on the Platform. To sell the product(s) you list for sale on the platform, you must be able to do so legally.</li>
                        <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt;">You must make sure that the product(s) on the list do not violate any third parties' intellectual property, trade secrets, other proprietary rights, publicity rights, or privacy rights. Only text de-scriptions, graphics, and images describing your product for sale are permitted in listings.</li>
                        <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt;"> Every product that is listed on the platform needs to be listed in the proper category. For the pur-pose of successfully completing sales, all listed Products must be kept in stock. You consent to follow any listing guidelines packaging Depot Store may occa-sionally communicate to you.</li>
                        <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt;">The product listing description must accurately reflect the details and condition of the item and must not be deceptive. You agree to return any money you may have received from the retailer if the product description does not accurately re-flect the state of the item.</li>
                        <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt;">You affirm, warrant, and agree that you will use the Platform's Services only for business and commercial purposes and will refrain from using the Platform to purchase goods or services for your own use or consumption. The Retailer may only use the Products you offer or sell throughthe Platform for resale or other commercial pur-poses; the Retailer may not use the Products for personal use or consumption.</li>
                    </ol>
                </li>
            </ol>
        </li>
    </ol>
    <p style="margin-top:14pt; margin-left:144pt;  line-height:normal; font-size:13.5pt; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:Roboto;">&nbsp;</span></p>
    <ol class="small-roman" start="2" type="i" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt;">
        <li style="margin-top:14pt; margin-left:95pt; line-height:normal; padding-left:13pt; font-family:Roboto; font-size:13.5pt; background-color:#ffffff;"><strong>Payment and Settlement Services</strong>
            <ol class="lower-alpha" type="a" style="margin-right:0pt; margin-left:0pt; padding-left:0pt;">
                <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt;">For each transaction on the Platform, we will offer the OEMs Payment and Settlement Services. packaging Depot Store has the right to use or engage the ser-vices of any third party service provider(s), sub-contractor(s), or agent(s) on any terms packaging Depot Store may deem appropriate, but packaging Depot Store shall remain liable to the OEM for the performance of its obli-gations to provide Payment and Settlement Ser-vices under these Terms.</li>
                <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt;">OEM understands and agrees that we are only serving in the capacity of a fiduciary when provid-ing the payment collection services, and we are not responsible for the legality of any payment transaction between the OEM and the Retailer.</li>
                <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt;">If we decide, in our sole discretion, that the trans-action you are engaging in is not genuine or sus-picious or fraudulent, we shall have the right to refuse to make payments to you or any third party.</li>
                <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt;">In relation to these Payment and Settlement Ser-vices, you hereby consent and agree to comply with any guidelines, instructions, requests, etc. that may be made by us, third-party banks or fi-nancial institutions, as the case may be, or a pay-ment system provider from time to time.</li>
                <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt;">We will settle the payments received from the Retailer after actual delivery of the order(s) to the designated bank account of OEM (or third party based on the instructions given by the OEM (if applicable)) within 20 (twenty) bank working days from the date of delivery of the Consignment to the Retailer or 2 working days after Expiry of Re-fund Period (whichever is later), where the settle-ment will be made on the working day which is a Tuesday or a Friday within the aforementioned

                    timeline. Provided that, in case of any returns re-quest raised by Retailer or any claims or disputes raised by Retailer, we reserve our right to with-hold the settlement of payments to OEM until the resolution of such return requests, claims or dis-putes, as the case may be.</li>
                <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt;">In any of the settlements methods, OEM (or third party as per the instructions received from OEM) will receive the amount (minus, any amount to be refunded to the Retailer and any taxes payable under applicable laws) within the aforesaid time-lines. It is clarified that any settlement of payment to the OEM shall be subject to applicable tax laws and packaging Depot Store may deduct or collect such taxes from the amount to be paid to the OEM in accordance with the provisions of applicable tax laws as set out under clause (h) and (i) below.</li>
                <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt;">In relation to the tax collection at source under applicable GST laws, as may be amended from time to time:</li>
                <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt;">In case of any mismatches on account of tax col-lection at source, OEM shall be required to pro-vide all relevant information to us, to correspond with the relevant authorities and also in case of any liability accruing on account of omission shall be OEM's obligation to pay such deficit.</li>
                <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt;"> OEM will provide the corresponding Harmonised System Nomenclature (HSN) code number and applicable GST rates for every product sold of the Platform. You accept that declaring the HSN and GST rates of the product is your responsibil-ity, and that in order to sell the product(s) on the Platform pre-declaring the respective HSN and GST rates shall be mandatory.</li>
                <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt;">OEM will be responsible to provide their correct GST registration number against which the tax collected at source (under GST laws) need to be reported by us. We shall not hold any responsibil-ity of incorrect disclosures of GST registration number and consequent loss of credits of tax col-lected at source in the hands of the OEM. In case any tax, interest or penalty is imposed on us, on account of incorrect disclosure of information by

                    the OEM, then such OEM shall indemnify us with respect to such tax, interest or penalty as may be levied by the GST authorities.</li>
                <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt;">We shall have the right to deduct or recover, as the case may be, tax deducted at source (“TDS”) as may be applicable under the applica-ble provisions of Income Tax Act,1961 (as may be amended from time to time) and as deter-mined by us in our sole discretion on transactions and / or payments through or facilitated by the Platform. In respect of TDS deducted and / or re-covered, we will provide certificate(s) evidencing and / or supporting the deposit of TDS in the pre-scribed format in accordance with the provisions of the Income Tax Act, 1961 (as may be amended from time to time). It is clarified that for this purpose, we will be entitled to rely upon the Permanent Account Number (“PAN”) and any other particulars provided to us and we shall have no obligation to validate or verify the same. In the event of any liability that may arise on ac-count of incorrect or incomplete particulars / de-tails being provided by OEM to us including inter-est, penalty or any other levies, we shall have the right to recover the same from the OEM in our sole discretion.</li>
                <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt;">l. OEM shall comply with all the applicable regula-tions/ laws in relation to cash transaction as stip-ulated under the applicable tax laws.</li>
                <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt;">We shall be entitled to recover from the OEM, from time to time, any amounts due from it or in-curred by us on account of the following, unless the same are caused on account of negligence, act or omission of our or its employees, officers etc.</li>
                <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt;">Chargeback of transactions;</li>
                <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt;"> Any penalty or charge which may be levied on us by any payment instrument or the clearing house i.e. Reserve Bank of India or its local clearing agent (as the case may be) arising, inter alia, for excessive chargeback of transactions or exces-sive failure of transactions or excessive Retailer disputes and/or any other reason;</li>
                <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt;">any amount due to us from the OEM.</li>
                <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt;">If there are reasonable grounds to suspect that a transaction has been conducted in breach of any applicable laws or is a fraudulent transaction, we shall be entitled to suspend or withhold the pay-ments of the OEM that are due to the OEM.</li>
                <li style="margin-left:23pt; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt;">In case of an occurrence of a chargeback event, we reserve our right to withhold the settlements to OEM, pending enquiries by the banks or any regulatory body till the resolution of such issues</li>
            </ol>
        </li>
    </ol>
