        <li style="margin-left:59pt;  line-height:normal; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt; background-color:#ffffff;">In consideration for any special services, other than the standard services provided by packaging Depot Store to the OEMs, which are based on variable parameters, packaging Depot Store may levy a vari-able charge to the OEMs as may be communicated to the OEMs from time to time.</li>
