        <li style="margin-left:59pt; line-height:normal; padding-left:13pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="font-family:'Roboto, sans-serif'; font-size:14pt;"></span> We will not be held responsible in any way for claims result-ing from any ofthe following: (a) your actions or inactions; (b) following instructions given by you or anyone acting on your behalf; (c) a government authority's act or order; (d) the inad-equate packing or labeling ofthe Shipment; (e) the nature or description ofthe Shipment; (f) riots, civil unrest, strikes, lock-outs, stoppages, or restraints of; (g) explosion, fire, flood or storm; (h) any cause which we could not avoid and the con-sequences whereof we could not prevent by the exercise of reasonable diligence; (i) any loss, miss-delivery, delay or damage to any Shipment; and/or (j) any dispute or claims be-tween the OEM and the Retailer including without limitation relating to the Shipment or Products hereunder.</li>
