        <li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p>Rights Granted. Business Associate shall have the non-exclusive right throughout the Territory, during the term, and acting as an independent intermediary, to promote and advertise the packaging Depot Store Platform to Retailers, in all commercial channels of distribution, including without limitation.</p></li>

            <li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p><strong></strong>Duties and Responsibilities. Business Associate shall</p>
