                    <li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p>conduct its business in a manner that always reflects favourably on the Services and the good name, goodwill and reputation of packaging Depot Store;</p></li>
                    <li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p>avoid deceptive, misleading or unethical practices, that are or might be detrimental to packaging Depot Store or the Platform, including false or misleading representations with regard to packaging Depot Store or the Platform. Business Associate shall not make any representations or warranties concerning prices, terms or delivery, specifications, features, capabilities or performance of the Services that are inconsistent with the Documentation, terms of payment, or conditions of sales except to the extent such representations are authorized in writing by packaging Depot Store.</p></li>
                    <li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p>Business Associate furthermore shall</p>
                        <ol class="numberText" type="1" class="awlist1" style="margin-right:0pt; margin-left:0pt; padding-left:0pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;">
                            <li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p>be responsible for itself, its employees’ and Companies (packaging Depot Store) compliances with this Agreement, including all applicable restrictions;</p></li>
                            <li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p>use commercially reasonable efforts to promote and expand the Services of the packaging Depot Store platform in the allocated Territory inaccordance with the terms and conditions of this Agreement and applicable Indian laws and Government Regulations;</p></li>
                            <li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p>Will be responsible to Meet Retailers, Daily MIS to company for all related information not meeting any of these duties and responsibilities may result in the immediate termination for cause of this Agreement by packaging Depot Store.</p></li>
                            </ol>
                        </li>

    </ol>
</li>
<li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p><strong>Branding Guidelines.</strong> Business Associate shall follow and fully comply with packaging Depot Store Branding Guidelines in connection with provision of Services to the Retailers. packaging Depot Store reserves the right to modify the Branding Guidelines from time to time and shall give the Business Associate notice of any such modification. Within thirty (30) days of receipt of notice of any modifications to the Branding Guidelines, Business Associate shall act to assure that all Services, Promotional Materials or other promotional matters related with the Services comply with the Branding Guidelines</p></li>
<li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p><strong>Reserved Rights. </strong> All rights not specifically granted to Business Associate hereunder are reserved by packaging Depot Store.</p></li>

