    <ol class="numberText" start="3"  type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt;">
        <li style="margin-top:14pt; margin-left:59pt;  line-height:normal; padding-left:13pt; font-family:Roboto; font-size:13.5pt; background-color:#ffffff;"><strong>Business Associate OBLIGATIONS</strong>
    
    
    
        <ol type="i" class="awlist1 small-roman" style="margin-right:0pt; margin-left:0pt; padding-left:0pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;">
            <li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p><strong> Onboarding Customers.</strong> Business Associate shall use commercially reasonable efforts to promote the packaging Depot Store Platform and to onboard Retailers having business presence in their territory, into the business of trading of products related to basic construction material, cladding, flooring, hardware, plumbing, electrical fittings, sanitary, furniture, decorative and other similar products, as customers on the packaging Depot Store Platform</p></li>
            <li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p>Business Associate shall use commercially reasonable efforts to promote the marketing of the packaging Depot Store Platform and shall use commercially reasonable efforts to convince and persuade Retailers to Purchase Products from the packaging Depot Store Platform. Except as expressly set forth herein or otherwise agreed in writing by the Parties. The Business Associate will be provided with some promotional, marketing, advertisement material free of cost. Business Associate shall submit to packaging Depot Store in advance, for packaging Depot Store’s prior approval, any marketing and Promotional Materials developed by the Business Associate related to the Business Services.</p></li>
            <li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p>Business Associate shall use commercially reasonable efforts to assist and support retailers in case of any issues with respect to the packaging Depot Store Portal or with issues in respect of the purchases made through the packaging Depot Store Portal or Payment related Issues for Purchase Conducted through the packaging Depot Store Platform.</p></li>
            <li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p>Business Associate shall verify the Goods Return Requests raised by the retailers and shall inspect the Goods requested for Return by the retailer. Only on satisfactory inspection of the goods, the Business Associate shall approve the Return of the Goods and intimate the same to the packaging Depot Store Platform.</li>
            <li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p>The Business Associate shall follow up with the Retailers for timely payment of purchases made on the Platform by the Retailers.</p></li>
            <li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p><strong>Pursuit of Accepted Opportunities.</strong>  Business Associate agrees to work collaboratively with packaging Depot Store at all times and, where requested by packaging Depot Store, Business Associate agrees to work under the direction of an packaging Depot Store senior representative.</p></li>
            <li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p><strong>Working Outside of Territory.</strong>  In the event a Business Associate is able to onboard retailers having additional business places outside of their territory Business Associate must obtain packaging Depot Store prior written consent to engage with such Retailer for onboarding them on the packaging Depot Store Platform. Business Associate is able to onboard retailers outside of their territory by creating a sub–CP outside his territory. Business Associate acknowledges that in such a case, specific rules of theapplicable Territory and/or packaging Depot Store specific guidelines and directions shall apply and supersede this Agreement.</p></li>
            <li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p><strong> packaging Depot Store Rights.</strong>  Other than rights granted herein, Business Associate acknowledges that nothing in this Agreement shall prevent or limit packaging Depot Store from marketing and selling its Services, in whole or in part, directly or indirectly, in the Territory or outside the Territory, to any prospective Retailers, or from working with sub-CP, other representatives, sellers, distributors or other marketing agents, without any liability to Business Associate.</p></li>
            <li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p><strong> Business Associate </strong> shall</p>
                <ol class="lower-alpha" type="a" class="awlist1" style="margin-right:0pt; margin-left:0pt; padding-left:0pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;">
                    <li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p>Train and maintain a sufficient number of capable technical and sales/pre-sales personnel having the knowledge and training necessary to</p>
                        <ol class="numberText" type="1" class="awlist1" style="margin-right:0pt; margin-left:0pt; padding-left:0pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;">
                            <li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p>inform Retailer properly concerning the features and capabilities of the packaging Depot Store Platform;</p></li>
                            <li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p>if applicable, provide the Training and Support to the Services in accordance with Business Associate's obligations;</p></li>
                            <li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p>Inform packaging Depot Store promptly and in writing of any facts or opinions regarding suspected Services defects, intellectual property infringement claims, customer complaints and/or other facts that may affect the performance of this Agreement or packaging Depot Store’s reputation or goodwill;</p></li>
                            <li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p>Promptly provide packaging Depot Store, as may be requested, with detailed information regarding</p>
                                <ol type="i" class="awlist1 small-roman" style="margin-right:0pt; margin-left:0pt; padding-left:0pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;">
