            <li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p><strong>Performance Period.</strong> Irrespective of the Term of this Agreement, the parties will set Business Associate performance review periods, for which Business Associate may earn specific incentives as set forth in the Business Associate Program (“Performance Period”). The Performance Period will be set for one (1) year, commencing on the Effective Date..</p></li>
