        <li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p><strong>Headings.</strong> The caption and the headings to clauses, sections, parts, paragraphs Partner Orders, Orders or seller Orders are inserted for convenience only and shall be ignored in interpreting this Agreement.</p>
        </li>
        <li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p><strong>Agreement Drafted by all Parties</strong>. This Agreement, which the Parties have agreed to draw up in the English language, is the result of arm’s length negotiations between the Parties and shall be construed to have been drafted by all Parties such that any ambiguities in this Agreement shall not be construed against either Party.</p>
