        <li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p><strong>Partner Commissions.</strong>  Once a OEM is onboarded on the packaging Depot Store Platform, The Partner shall be eligible for commission on all Sells made on the packaging Depot Store Platform by the said OEM after being onboarded by the Partner, except for Sells made by the said OEM to Sellers with whom the said OEM have an Existing Business Relationship prior to the Said OEM being onboarded on the packaging Depot Store Platform.</p></li>
