                <li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p>Partner Commission shall be based on the percentage of Net Value of the Sells (Net Value shall be Sells values exclusive of Taxes, Logistic Charges, Discounts and any Schemes) made by the OEM, onboarded on the platform by the Growth Partner. Partner Commission is based on the rates as set forth in the Growth Partner Program.</li>
                <li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p>Partner Commission shall become due only once 15 days have passed from the expiry of the Return Period.</li>
                <li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p>Payment of the Partner Commission shall be made by Bank transfer subject to deduction of Direct and Indirect Taxes.</li>
                <li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p>Due Commission Shall be paid to the Partners post reduction of recoveries, if any from the Partner.</li>
