        </li>
        <li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p><strong>Taxes.</strong> The Growth Partner will bear all taxes and duties which may be levied with respect to the payment of the Partner Commission by packaging Depot Store.</p></li>
        <li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p><strong>Expenses.</strong> The Growth Partner will bear all expenses and travel costs it may incur with respect to the performance of this Agreement.</p></li>
