                <li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p>any assigned OEM onboarded by / assigned to the Growth Partner hereunder may be transferred to another Growth Partner in packaging Depot Store’S sole discretion. Termination or expiration is not an exclusive remedy and all other remedies will be available whether or not termination occurs.</p></li>
            </ol>
        </li>
        <li style="margin-left:31.65pt; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:normal; background-color:#ffffff;"><p><strong> Performance Period.</strong>  Irrespective of the Term of this Agreement, the parties will set Growth Partner performance review periods, for which Growth Partner may earn specific incentives as set forth in the Growth Partner Program (“Performance Period”). The Performance Period will be set for one (1) year, commencing on the Effective Date.</p></li>
